 in a serving dish, top with chicken involtini and serve immediately garnished with fresh parsley."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto","content":["70 g olive oil","40 g Parmesan cheese, cut in pieces (2 cm)","1 garlic clove","160 g pine nuts","100 g sun-dried tomatoes in oil, drained"]},{"title":"Chicken Involtini","content":["70 g mozzarella cheese, cut in pieces (4 cm)","2 garlic cloves","2 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only, plus extra for garnishing","2 medium eggs","1 pinch fine sea salt, or to taste","1 pinch ground black pepper, or to taste","70 g breadcrumbs","15 chicken breast fillets","30 fresh spinach leaves, large stalks removed"]},{"title":"Sauce","content":["1 garlic clove","75 g onions, quartered","50 g olive oil","650 - 700 g tomato passata"]}],"id":"r113161","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-ViYLS8R4FA8\/XZQxHEjHKtI\/AAAAAAAAcr4\/q2bNt5L-6MgBQ56ncMy0rXxvL4DAgldtgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_lx58xnPsG4KJoKvC.png","title":"Chicken Involtini with Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto","publishedAt":"2017-02-06T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"40 g","fat":"47.1 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"27.1 g","calories":"2950 kJ \/ 702 kcal"},"usefulItems":"jug, airtight jar or container, cocktail stick, meat mallet or rolling pin, serving dish, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Vegetables of choice can be steamed on the Varoma tray at the same time as chicken involtini if desired. This may affect cooking time for the chicken so check it is cooked through and extend cooking time accordingly if required.","To store leftover sun-dried tomato pesto, transfer to an airtight container, then top with a thin layer of olive oil until pesto is covered. Place in fridge until required."],"basicInfo":["medium","25m","50m","5 portions"]}